social_posts.post_text: From the Christmas 2022 Photo Album 📕🎄❤️
BRIsbane
Living my Ariel fantasy 🧜🏼‍♀️
Last day here💗☀️🇦🇺

A trip to remember ✨🥂💽

In October I entered a contest run by @fronterawines @fronterawinescanada (the wine sponsor for The Grammys) that popped up as an ad on my Instagram story for the chance to win an all expense payed trip to the biggest night in music: The Grammys. I couldn’t believe it when I found out I won. 

Huge thank you to @fronterawines for the most memorable and amazing weekend of my life and for such a VIP experience ✨🥂

And so grateful to have been able to share this experience with @c_schiefner 😘❤️
#fronteragrammys #fronteraexperience #grammyawards
Some more photos from this unforgettable weekend with @fronterawines 💫🍷 #fronteraexperience #fronteragrammys #grammyawards
A piece I made in October and then never got around to filming it … so ya, here it is now 🖤 #brimapschoreo

School Spirits out now on @paramountplus 💙🤍💙 

Had such a blast working on this one last summer/fall with the best squad! ✨ Go Split River! 📣 

Choreographer: @lou.sky 
Assistant Choreographer: @ttempura 

Cheer Squad: @yudycamila @brittany_spiteri @briggsgibbins @hannahshaira_cam @hallegall @rainbowwedell @ali.g.thornton @vanessaprasad 

And big thank you to @brendacampbell_talentagent @ptmdance @premieretalentmanagement 💫

Second slide is how I feel about the first 5 episodes of Grease @riseofthepinkladies 💗🥹

If you haven’t watched yet, go get caught up now and use code PINKLADIES for a free month of @paramountplus 🙌🏻

Last year I had the absolute BEST 6 months working on this show as a background actor, as well as having a dancer role in Episode 6 (Next week’s episode ahhhh 🙈)! I loved Grease so much growing up so it was truly a dream come true to be part of this new series that takes place 4 years before the original. The music and dances are absolutely phenomenal and the entire cast and crew put their whole heart into everything. I made so many amazing friends working on this show, and how could you not when you’re working 14 hour days, almost 5 days a week together 😂❤️

Also p.s. I decided to name my character Scarlett 💅🏼💁🏼‍♀️
It’s picnic season!!! ☀️☀️☀️

@riseofthepinkladies EPISODE 6 out now!! 💛

This number “Girls Can’t Drive” was such a fun and wild one to be a part of! I’m so honoured and grateful to have been able to dance and do what I love on this amazing show, surrounded by so much talent 🥹💗 Not to mention it was such a special episode being @jamizzi’s directorial debut 🤩👏🏻

Big thanks to the whole choreo team @jamizzi @jeffreymortensen & @lou.sky (who, by the way, is the one swinging from the chandelier!!!) 💛

And of course a big thank you to my agent @brendacampbell_talentagent @ptmdance 🫶🏻💫

On Wednesdays we wear pink 💅🏼💗

A couple headshots by @vancouverheadshotphotographer 📸

EPISODE 8 OF @riseofthepinkladies OUT NOW 💗

The Fall Ball was WILD, you guys don’t want to miss this one!! I can’t even begin to describe how much fun we had on these shoots, despite the long hours through the nights, and shooting during heat waves in the daytime. When you’re surrounding by that much amazing energy, talent, and passion, everything feels like a dream. 

The fabulous show runner @annabeloakes directed this one and WOW did it ever turn out magical 👏🏻😍

I keep saying this, but this was my fav episode!! (Also had a pretty great prom date🙊😉) 

USE CODE PINKLADIES FOR A FREE MONTH OF PARAMOUNT+ (which means if you sign up now you’ll be able to watch the rest of the episodes!!)

DREAM MOMS on @hallmarkchannel 👑💜 

Had such a blast working on this one back in February with such an amazing group of dancers, the wonderful @melenadance as choreographer, and directed by  @jessicanoelleharmon 💃🏼👏🏻✨

Thank you to everyone for making this such a fun day and project to work on, and thank you to my agent @brendacampbell_talentagent @ptmdance 🫶🏻
Fun fact: I thrifted this skirt, and turns out it was @bellymtee’s that she donated 😂🖤🤍
Getting my sparkle back ✨
She really is that girl 🤩👑🐝😭 Such an unreal night, and a concert that has always been a dream of mine to see ✨  #renaissance
Wishing you the happiest birthday @c_schiefner 😘❤️ Thank you for constantly filling my life with so much love and laughter everyday, and for being my best friend 🥹 Love you ❤️🥐
